channel.title: Cannot find path specified?
channel.description:
i just got a new laptop, and im tryna run it from it.. i downloaded jdk update 5. i downloaded no-ip. i port forwarded. i tried using this compiler.. [code]@echo off color 0a title vipscape Compiler "C:Program FilesJavajdk1.6.0_05injavac.exe" *.java pause[/code]
and it says cannot find path specified... i go to my computer... hereds classpath [code]CLASSPATH=C:Program FilesJavajdk1.6.0_05in;%CLASSPATH%;[/code]
and heres path [code]C:Program FilesJavajdk1.6.0_05in[/code] so uh..why doesnt it work?
